    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# 🛠️ Setup Guide  \n\n👉 **Setup Guide (n8n + Vapi)** (Copy Link) [Google Doc](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Uq97UWyLrJdBqu0EgWdIm8xumTzB3M3h5g9PVYk4kqs/copy)\n\nFollow the steps below to get this workflow up and running:\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Step 1: Add Your [VAPI](https://vapi.ai/) API Key  \n- Grab your API key from VAPI  \n- In n8n, create a **Generic Credential** using **Bearer Auth**  \n- Paste your VAPI API key into the **two HTTP Request** nodes that require VAPI\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Step 2: Add the System Prompt to Your VAPI Assistant  \n- Open your VAPI Assistant settings  \n- Copy/paste the system prompt from this doc:  \n  👉 **System Prompt (Copy Link):** [Google Doc](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1d6ttmjqUokaVveISogTwyzI-oKYrEKh2J4AqUGvCyMU/copy)\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Step 3: Connect a Phone Number in VAPI  \n- Connect (or purchase) a phone number inside VAPI  \n- In the **Call Lead** HTTP Request node, make sure you set:  \n  - **Your Assistant ID**  \n  - **Your Phone Number ID**\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Step 4: Connect the Google Sheet Template  \n- Make a copy of the template here:  \n  👉 **Google Sheet Template (Copy Link):** [Google Sheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/1/d/1NEEmrQhRC0cGLyYKa0qTr5e72Iub38_tZFs4l37PwTk/copy)  \n- Connect your Google credentials in n8n  \n- Point the workflow to **your copied sheet** (not the original template)\n\n---\n\n### 💡 Final Check  \nBefore running, confirm:\n- VAPI key is present in both required HTTP Request nodes  \n- Assistant ID + Phone Number ID are correctly set in **Call Lead**  \n- Google Sheet connection points to your copied template\n",
        "height": 1072,
        "width": 784
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -656,
